name: "The Last Supper" Kalamint Secondary Market Auction Screenshot
description: https://kalamint.io/token/4626    After a dramatic bidding war with @LongShotParadox, "The Last Supper", by Victoria West (VictoriaWestPortrait.com), was bought on a Kalamint Auction on May 24th, 2021 by judgeman @judgeman_xtz for 385 xtz. It was relisted on the secondary market and sold for 666 xtz to @LongShotParadox on May 27th, 2021, for 666 xtz.
